1. *Krov* je izrađen od čelika. (The roof is made of steel.)
2. *Krov* je prekriven šindrom. (The roof is covered with shingles.)
3. Obnovili smo *krov* na stari zgradi. (We have renovated the roof of the old building.)
4. U ovoj kući ima tri *krova*. (This house has three roofs.)
5. Na *krovu* se nalazi lepa terasa. (There is a beautiful terrace on the roof.)